  "title": "Xtra Crunchy Croatian Shiitake Mushrooms Skewers",
  "description": "A funky and cozy Croatian dish featuring shiitake mushrooms with a char-grill flavor, ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients, and a crunchy texture.",
